    <item>
      <title>中国最大券商在股市暴跌后限制卖空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-s-biggest-brokerage-restricts-short-sales-after-stock-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于中国股市进一步暴跌，中国最大的券商已暂停对内地市场部分客户的卖空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-s-biggest-brokerage-restricts-short-sales-after-stock-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:56:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股市下跌，中国共同基金以五年来最快速度崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-mutual-fund-liquidations-hit-five-year-high-as-stocks-sink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市的暴跌正在对该国的资产管理行业造成严重破坏，将共同基金关闭数量推至五年来新高，这是投资者信心减弱的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-mutual-fund-liquidations-hit-five-year-high-as-stocks-sink</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:43:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券的地震转变让交易者密切关注收益率曲线的一举一动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/when-will-the-treasury-yield-curve-return-to-normal-and-steepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员越来越相信，美国国债收益率即将恢复到其存在以来大部分时间的交易方式——使金融市场保持反弹的是正常化的方式、原因和时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/when-will-the-treasury-yield-curve-return-to-normal-and-steepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 ETF 带动的热情消退，比特币跌至一个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/bitcoin-btc-retreats-to-one-month-low-as-etf-led-enthusiasm-wanes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对新交易所交易基金的炒作引发的对代币的投机需求消散，比特币跌至 12 月中旬以来的最低水平，导致该加密货币自 2024 年初以来一直处于亏损状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/bitcoin-btc-retreats-to-one-month-low-as-etf-led-enthusiasm-wanes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 22:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电涨势提振情绪，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市上涨，因台积电的前景激发了对该行业全球复苏的希望，在交易员寻找有关美联储下一步行动的线索之际提振了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 22:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
